Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.02,0:00:08.26,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.26,0:00:09.43,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to go to the nurse's office?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.06,0:00:16.20,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.20,0:00:17.99,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She seems to be feeling unwell.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.05,0:00:20.02,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.17,0:00:27.26,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you show up yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.14,0:00:30.40,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't we going to review our behavior on Saturday?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.40,0:00:31.82,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.82,0:00:34.21,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I did the reviewing by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.66,0:00:36.14,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Upon asking...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.14,0:00:38.23,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...I learned that after school yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.23,0:00:41.38,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...Haruhi had gone back over the course her team had taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.38,0:00:43.17,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hot. I'm exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.17,0:00:45.35,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,When do we change uniforms?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:47.44,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to change into the summer uniform as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.44,0:00:48.67,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzumiya...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.67,0:00:50.83,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I've probably said this already...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.83,0:00:53.98,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...but how about you give up on looking for mysterious things you're not going to find...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.98,0:00:57.02,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...and try having fun the way a normal high schooler does?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.45,0:00:59.61,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,How does a normal high schooler have fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.85,0:01:01.55,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Find some nice guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.55,0:01:03.99,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...and do your city searching with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.99,0:01:05.06,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You could even call it a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.06,0:01:06.20,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill two birds with one stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.50,0:01:09.20,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Men are worthless.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.53,0:01:12.91,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Feelings of love are just a temporary lapse in judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.91,0:01:14.87,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Like a kind of mental illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.38,0:01:16.69,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Even I...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.69,0:01:19.78,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...get in the mood for that stuff every now and then.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.78,0:01:21.93,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I am a healthy young girl, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.93,0:01:24.13,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,My body has its urges.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.13,0:01:25.09,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.09,0:01:29.93,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not stupid enough to let a moment's slip-up leave me saddled with a huge burden.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.72,0:01:33.72,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, if I start shopping around for guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.72,0:01:35.62,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...what will happen to the SOS Brigade?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.62,0:01:37.81,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I've only just made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.81,0:01:40.99,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You could turn it into some random club that just has fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.99,0:01:42.48,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll get people to join that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.81,0:01:43.74,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.74,0:01:47.03,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I made the SOS Brigade because that kind of club is no fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.03,0:01:50.29,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I even recruited an alluring mascot and a mysterious transfer student.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.29,0:01:52.61,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why doesn't anything happen!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.72,0:01:56.91,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if some kind of full-blown trouble will happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.62,0:01:59.63,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say such dangerous things!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.52,0:02:01.87,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.56,0:02:06.63,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If something happened to make everyday life more interesting...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.63,0:02:07.84,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...that could be quite wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.24,0:02:14.12,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's the first time I've seen Haruhi look so defeated...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.12,0:02:16.52,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...but her crestfallen face was surprisingly cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.79,0:02:19.88,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps Suzumiya-san is feeling lovesick?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.88,0:02:20.60,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Definitely not.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.40,0:02:23.61,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Suzumiya isn't going to suddenly fall in love...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.61,0:02:26.91,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and her full-blown trouble isn't going to happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.91,0:02:29.35,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At least not any time soon, in this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.86,0:02:32.42,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But the full-blown trouble part...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.42,0:02:34.60,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...had already begun brewing in the shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.82,0:02:48.80,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As I talked to Haruhi that morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.45,0:02:51.42,HaruhiTitleOverlay,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3\fs26\fad(490,460)\pos(632,388)\fscx90}The Melancholy of Haruhi Suzumiya IV
