Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.61,0:03:17.85,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.85,0:03:20.29,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...the handwriting obviously isn't Nagato's.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.29,0:03:23.07,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And she probably wouldn't use such a direct method...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.07,0:03:24.33,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...as placing a message in my shoe locker.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.83,0:03:26.45,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Could it be Asahina-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.32,0:03:28.99,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I doubt that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.99,0:03:33.85,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't see her using some ripped out scrap of paper to call me out without setting a specific time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.17,0:03:36.46,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}It's so hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.69,0:03:36.46,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Haruhi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.93,0:03:38.17,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even less likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.17,0:03:42.87,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She'd just drag me up the stairs to talk again like that other time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.87,0:03:45.07,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Koizumi's out for similar reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.39,0:03:47.82,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like an air conditioner in this room!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.82,0:03:50.55,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I really doubt that this is a love letter...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.55,0:03:53.10,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...but it's certain that this document is requesting my presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.41,0:03:54.39,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Or no.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.39,0:03:57.02,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It could just be Taniguchi or Kunikida pulling a prank on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.45,0:03:58.33,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.33,0:04:00.04,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's the most feasible possiblity.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.04,0:04:01.32,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But if that was the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.32,0:04:04.28,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...I would expect something more elaborate...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.71,0:04:05.30,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.30,0:04:05.87,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.20,0:04:07.66,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What? They're pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.66,0:04:09.76,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Knockout pictures of Mikuru-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.76,0:04:11.23,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.23,0:04:12.34,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing with those!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.34,0:04:15.09,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm putting them on the top page of our site!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.09,0:04:18.48,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This will bring in lots of e-mails about strange happenings.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.48,0:04:20.66,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And our access counter will jump...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.66,0:04:22.85,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...up to five digits in a flash!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.65,0:04:25.72,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if the counter can support that many digits.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.72,0:04:26.43,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.43,0:04:26.97,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.96,0:04:29.82,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, stupid Kyon!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.82,0:04:30.68,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop acting like an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.41,0:04:34.29,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If Asahina-san found out that unbecoming pictures of her maid costume...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.29,0:04:35.59,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...in knockout poses...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.59,0:04:37.81,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...have been spread around the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.81,0:04:40.32,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...she'll definitely faint on the spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.67,0:04:43.09,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oddly enough, Haruhi quietly stared at me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.09,0:04:45.45,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...as I fervently lectured her...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.45,0:04:49.51,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...but it's unknown if she understood what I meant by the dangers of putting personal information...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.51,0:04:52.02,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...that may reveal your identity on the Internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.38,0:04:53.24,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it.
