Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.83,0:05:06.63,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.97,0:05:10.46,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going home for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.47,0:05:18.68,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.81,0:05:24.18,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.18,0:05:26.02,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.02,0:05:28.15,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,An evil plot was thwarted.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.82,0:05:31.31,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Having nothing to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.31,0:05:33.04,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...I was playing Othello with Asahina-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.04,0:05:34.19,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...when Koizumi showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.54,0:05:35.78,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With his usual smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.78,0:05:37.11,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.11,0:05:38.41,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be excusing myself now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.69,0:05:41.91,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And what kind of work would that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.61,0:05:46.57,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to change...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.57,0:05:48.03,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...so you can go home first.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.03,0:05:50.46,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And so I took Asahina-san up on her offer...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.46,0:05:51.96,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and hightailed it out of the clubroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.69,0:05:59.77,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When I saw the person standing there...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.77,0:06:01.62,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...I was considerably surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.88,0:06:06.77,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.97,0:06:09.04,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.49,0:06:11.22,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.22,0:06:12.02,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't expect me, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.17,0:06:14.41,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.79,0:06:16.99,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There is something I need you for...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.71,0:06:19.82,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But I want to ask you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.89,0:06:22.62,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about Suzumiya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.44,0:06:24.41,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.41,0:06:25.60,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.60,0:06:26.79,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Another Suzumiya fan, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.50,0:06:28.74,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.74,0:06:33.09,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Humans always say, "It's better to regret something you did than to regret something you didn't do."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.49,0:06:34.84,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your opinion on that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.26,0:06:38.30,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know about it being a common saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.30,0:06:39.72,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...but it probably means what it says.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.24,0:06:41.26,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.26,0:06:42.84,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking theoretically...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.84,0:06:46.76,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If there were a situation where maintaining the status quo would only make things worse...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.76,0:06:50.97,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...but nobody knew what course of action would improve circumstances...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.97,0:06:52.27,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...what would you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.78,0:06:54.15,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.15,0:06:55.81,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you talking about the Japanese economy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.31,0:06:59.88,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't you think that change, any change at all, would be best for now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.88,0:07:02.57,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing will improve the way things currently are.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.57,0:07:05.03,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess that's one way to look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.03,0:07:05.94,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.48,0:07:08.56,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.56,0:07:11.57,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...the higher-ups are all stick-in-the-muds who can't keep up with change.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.99,0:07:14.03,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't afford such complacency out in the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.03,0:07:17.08,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A lack of action would only allow the situation to grow worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.73,0:07:22.29,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, it should be okay for me to use my own judgment to assert changes, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.61,0:07:24.27,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is she trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.27,0:07:25.27,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is this a prank?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.27,0:07:27.88,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is Taniguchi hiding in the broom closet or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.48,0:07:30.80,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I've grown quite tired...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.80,0:07:32.76,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...of observing a static subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.76,0:07:33.39,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.39,0:07:36.39,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'll kill you and see how Haruhi Suzumiya responds.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.13,0:07:43.52,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait, wait, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.52,0:07:44.64,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.64,0:07:45.42,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.42,0:07:46.62,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.62,0:07:49.59,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why is Asakura trying to stab me with a knife?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.59,0:07:50.32,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hold on a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.32,0:07:51.49,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What did Asakura say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.49,0:07:53.07,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.07,0:07:53.99,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why? For what reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.99,0:07:55.26,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop joking around!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.26,0:07:56.44,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's really dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.44,0:07:58.91,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A fake would be enough to scare anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.91,0:08:00.70,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You think that this is a joke?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.71,0:08:04.18,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.18,0:08:05.59,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want to be killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.59,0:08:10.27,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really understand the concept of death for organic life forms.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.27,0:08:12.12,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it! It's not funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.12,0:08:14.22,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Just put that dangerous thing down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.74,0:08:16.47,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.15,0:08:19.98,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I truly want you to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.83,0:08:27.11,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.39,0:08:30.40,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This space is now under my data jurisdiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.94,0:08:32.91,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No one can leave or enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.36,0:08:35.34,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have no idea what's going on anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.34,0:08:36.94,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If somebody does, come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.94,0:08:38.16,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And explain this to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.65,0:08:40.36,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, just give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.36,0:08:42.37,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The result will be the same in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.33,0:08:44.92,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.20,0:08:55.30,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.30,0:08:56.48,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.48,0:09:00.10,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now everything in this classroom moves according to my will.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.47,0:09:01.94,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait! Wait! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.94,0:09:03.13,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.13,0:09:05.23,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kill me and see how Haruhi Suzumiya responds?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.53,0:09:06.72,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Haruhi again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.72,0:09:08.24,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You sure are popular Haruhi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.24,0:09:08.76,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.76,0:09:10.87,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why does that mean I have to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.87,0:09:12.90,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I should have done this to start with.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.09,0:09:16.29,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My body won't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.29,0:09:16.82,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You can do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.82,0:09:17.82,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I cry foul play!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.82,0:09:19.15,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If you die...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.15,0:09:22.11,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...Suzumiya-san is certain to take some sort of action.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.66,0:09:26.03,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll probably be able to observe a considerable explosion of data.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.03,0:09:27.45,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A golden opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.83,0:09:29.14,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.33,0:09:31.66,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Now die.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.29,0:09:38.41,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurt, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.41,0:09:39.03,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.34,0:09:39.94,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.94,0:09:41.26,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can move now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.00,0:09:44.59,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagato?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.69,0:09:52.14,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Your individual programs were too weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.14,0:09:55.59,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The spatial lockdown and data blockade in lateral sectors were too weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.59,0:09:57.55,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That is why I could detect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.55,0:09:58.56,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why intrusion was granted.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.94,0:10:00.22,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to get in my way?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.54,0:10:02.32,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If this human is killed...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.32,0:10:04.74,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...Haruhi Suzumiya is certain to act.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.74,0:10:07.41,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the only way to obtain more data.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.82,0:10:10.22,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You are supposed to be my backup.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.22,0:10:12.59,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Independent action has not been authorized.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.59,0:10:14.43,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You are supposed to obey me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.43,0:10:15.96,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't want to?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.96,0:10:17.63,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I will nullify your data link.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.95,0:10:19.11,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead and try?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.11,0:10:21.30,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I have the advantage in this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.30,0:10:23.96,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This classroom is now within space under my data jurisdiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.39,0:10:26.89,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I am requisitioning the nullification of your data link.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.22,0:10:34.45,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That was when...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.45,0:10:38.52,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...I thought, "Ah, they really aren't human."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.93,0:10:46.82,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay close.
