Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.21,0:11:04.59,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll cease functioning before that happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.88,0:11:06.59,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.94,0:11:11.78,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how long you can last while protecting that thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.60,0:11:28.62,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagato!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.60,0:11:31.06,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no need for you to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.48,0:11:32.48,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I am fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.23,0:11:34.24,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.24,0:11:35.94,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You don't look fine at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.70,0:11:43.68,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you've suffered so much damage...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.68,0:11:46.43,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...you won't be able to interfere with other data.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.81,0:11:47.96,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll end this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.18,0:11:50.21,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Die.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.42,0:11:58.36,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.98,0:12:00.23,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.23,0:12:02.34,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The three years of your brief life?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.86,0:12:03.67,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.98,0:12:05.89,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Commence nullification of data link.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.32,0:12:13.19,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.11,0:12:15.89,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You are exceptionally skilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.89,0:12:19.60,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That is why it took so long to force a program into this space.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.49,0:12:21.66,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But it is finished now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.55,0:12:26.16,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You prepared dissolution factors before you infiltrated this space.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.69,0:12:29.11,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That would explain why you seemed too weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.41,0:12:32.67,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You had already expended your offensive data before we began.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.81,0:12:34.86,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pity.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.86,0:12:37.33,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose I was only ever backup.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.06,0:12:42.05,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it would be a good chance to end this stasis.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.55,0:12:44.78,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I've lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.78,0:12:45.71,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.71,0:12:46.99,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You get to live a while longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.99,0:12:48.64,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But you'd best be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.64,0:12:49.98,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.98,0:12:52.91,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...the Integration Thought Entity has its dissenting voices.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.63,0:12:57.37,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Another agent from the radical faction may come one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.37,0:13:00.99,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Or, Nagato-san's master may switch views.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.00,0:13:04.20,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Enjoy your time with Suzumiya-san until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.69,0:13:05.61,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.08,0:13:10.06,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Nagato!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.70,0:13:11.38,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.38,0:13:12.56,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll call an ambulance!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.56,0:13:13.33,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No need.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.33,0:13:15.89,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,My body did not suffer significant injury.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.89,0:13:19.30,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This space is what must be normalized first.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.30,0:13:22.26,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I will remove foreign substances and reconstruct the classroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.63,0:13:33.19,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.71,0:13:37.33,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Processing power was redirected to data manipulation and transformation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.33,0:13:40.16,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The regeneration of this interface was placed in queue.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.52,0:13:42.96,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's running now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.77,0:13:44.36,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.23,0:13:49.32,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot to reconstruct glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.07,0:13:52.47,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd say you look cuter without them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.47,0:13:54.51,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm not really a glasses man.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.51,0:13:56.03,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What is a glasses man?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.04,0:13:58.06,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.06,0:13:58.87,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just babbling.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.66,0:14:01.58,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.91,0:14:03.36,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,'Sup.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.36,0:14:05.75,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,For-For-For-Forgot my...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.44,0:14:08.29,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.29,0:14:09.56,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you look at this still-frame...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.56,0:14:12.76,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...my position would suggest that I'm actually trying to push her down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.41,0:14:14.24,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,My bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.05,0:14:15.97,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Enjoy yourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.00,0:14:18.26,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,An interesting person.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.02,0:14:21.67,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.67,0:14:22.86,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.86,0:14:24.35,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I specialize in data manipulation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.92,0:14:27.40,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I have made it so Ryoko Asakura has transferred out of this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.40,0:14:28.40,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's your concern?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.83,0:14:30.75,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Or this isn't the time for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.75,0:14:32.23,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now that I stop and think about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.23,0:14:34.60,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...I just went through an incredible experience, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.93,0:14:37.88,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That winding freak talk of Nagato's the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.88,0:14:41.59,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is no longer about whether or not I believe that delusional story.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.59,0:14:45.95,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was about ready to piss my pants during the incident just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.95,0:14:47.52,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was seriously about to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.52,0:14:51.08,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Doesn't this mean that I have no choice but to accept that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.08,0:14:53.01,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...Nagato is genuinely related to aliens or whatever?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.69,0:14:59.29,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\an8}Ryoko Asakura didn't show up for class the next day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.05,0:14:57.96,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This concerns Asakura-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.96,0:15:00.84,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Due to her father's work...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.84,0:15:03.21,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...I also find this rather sudden...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.21,0:15:04.46,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...she has transferred to another school.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.46,0:15:05.18,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.65,0:15:08.47,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.47,0:15:09.48,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's up here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.89,0:15:12.30,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Haruhi Suzumiya, who had completely bounced back...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.30,0:15:13.92,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...looked at me with shining eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.92,0:15:14.75,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.75,0:15:15.69,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tell her the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.58,0:15:18.95,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Like hell I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.95,0:15:20.49,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not like I even want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.49,0:15:23.55,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I would prefer to think that it was all a hallucination.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.22,0:15:26.50,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,First a mysterious transfer student came...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.50,0:15:29.94,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...now we have a girl transferring out for no explicable reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.94,0:15:32.06,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This matter needs some investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.06,0:15:34.17,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'd like it if you didn't give me more work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.48,0:15:35.79,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've already got enough problems...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.79,0:15:38.47,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...without you adding on to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.09,0:15:40.23,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.23,0:15:41.01,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.47,0:15:43.16,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The other matter on my mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.16,0:15:45.72,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...was another envelope just like yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.72,0:15:47.71,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...in my shoe locker.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.71,0:15:48.74,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's up with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.74,0:15:51.88,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is putting letters in shoe lockers the current fad?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.88,0:15:54.98,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But today's is considerably different.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.19,0:15:54.98,HaruhiNoteMikuru,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs60\bord0.2\b0\c&H76826D&\3c&H76826D&\frz-26\pos(287,325)}Mikuru Asahina
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.78,0:15:58.74,HaruhiNoteMikuru,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs40\bord0.2\b0\c&H76826D&\3c&H76826D&\frz-14.3\pos(520,172)}I'll be waiting in the clubroom
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.78,0:15:58.74,HaruhiNoteMikuru,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs40\bord0.2\b0\c&H76826D&\3c&H76826D&\frz-14.3\pos(579,230)}during lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.78,0:15:58.74,HaruhiNoteMikuru,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs46\bord0.2\b0\c&H76826D&\3c&H76826D&\frz-16\pos(323,418)}Mikuru
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.17,0:15:58.74,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I briskly went on my way...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.74,0:16:02.48,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...hoping to be spared another life-threatening experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.90,0:16:05.67,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, I have no choice but to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.67,0:16:07.74,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The person who sent this is none other than Asahina-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.60,0:16:12.24,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}While I had no evidence to prove that this letter was actually from Asahina-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.24,0:16:13.74,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...I didn't doubt its origins for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.44,0:16:17.35,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She seems just like the kind of person to use such a roundabout method...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.35,0:16:20.98,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and the image of her cheerfully writing on a sheet of cute stationery...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.98,0:16:23.21,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...fits her perfectly, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.21,0:16:26.14,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And Nagato's also in the clubroom during lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.14,0:16:27.76,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, it'll work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.89,0:16:30.91,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.91,0:16:34.10,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyon-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.44,0:16:36.49,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.60,0:16:40.06,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She looks just like Asahina-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.06,0:16:42.73,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But it wasn't Asahina-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.23,0:16:44.19,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.19,0:16:45.98,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you Asahina-san's sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.38,0:16:49.82,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.82,0:16:51.83,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The real Mikuru Asahina.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.83,0:16:55.87,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm from a later future than the me you're familiar with.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.39,0:16:57.20,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I've missed you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.56,0:17:01.57,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't believe me, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.57,0:17:02.71,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll prove it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.23,0:17:04.09,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.09,0:17:06.52,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a star-shaped mole here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.52,0:17:07.97,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.97,0:17:08.80,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to touch it to make sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.80,0:17:09.34,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Super size me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.98,0:17:11.47,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you believe me now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.47,0:17:13.29,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's not the issue here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.29,0:17:15.99,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't know where Asahina-san has moles on her body.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.99,0:17:18.53,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The only times I've seen that much of her skin...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.53,0:17:20.83,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...would be when she was dressed up as a bunny girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.83,0:17:23.78,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and when I accidentally walked in on her changing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.78,0:17:27.02,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In either case, I didn't have enough time to make any detailed observations.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.62,0:17:28.60,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.60,0:17:32.05,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But weren't you the one who told me I had a mole here, Kyon-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.05,0:17:34.07,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't even notice it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.70,0:17:36.59,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.59,0:17:37.63,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.63,0:17:38.90,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.90,0:17:40.34,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It hasn't happened yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.96,0:17:42.48,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What do I do!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.48,0:17:44.71,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I've made a huge mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.71,0:17:45.60,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.60,0:17:47.09,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Please forget what I just said!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.09,0:17:48.34,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Easier said than done.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.72,0:17:50.10,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.10,0:17:51.78,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll believe you for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.78,0:17:56.52,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I've become a person who's ready to believe anything at this point...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.52,0:17:57.30,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.30,0:18:00.60,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean there are two Asahina-sans in this period right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.72,0:18:03.66,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.66,0:18:04.86,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The past me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.86,0:18:07.48,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...past from my point of view...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.48,0:18:10.80,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...is currently having lunch with classmates in the classroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.16,0:18:13.99,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I needed to tell you something...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.99,0:18:16.95,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...so I made some unreasonable requests in order to return to this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.07,0:18:20.55,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked Nagato-san to leave us alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.55,0:18:23.40,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know about Nagato?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.40,0:18:24.38,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.38,0:18:25.65,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's classified information.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.01,0:18:29.11,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't gotten to say that in a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.11,0:18:31.48,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I just heard it a few days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.25,0:18:37.83,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stay in this time very long.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.83,0:18:39.09,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'll be brief.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.25,0:18:41.84,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what Snow White is?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.99,0:18:44.74,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.74,0:18:48.48,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,When you find yourself in a harrowing situation...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.48,0:18:50.62,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...please remember those words.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.62,0:18:54.78,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean the story with seven dwarfs, a witch, and a poisoned apple?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.78,0:18:55.81,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.81,0:18:57.69,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember the story of Snow White.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.69,0:19:01.10,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just in a harrowing situation yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.10,0:19:02.69,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I'm talking about...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.69,0:19:03.75,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.75,0:19:05.06,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.06,0:19:06.93,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell you any specifics...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.93,0:19:10.24,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...but Suzumiya-san should be with you when it happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.96,0:19:12.22,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruhi and me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.22,0:19:13.00,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,When? Where!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.83,0:19:15.42,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzumiya-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.42,0:19:19.51,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...may not find anything wrong with the situation...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.51,0:19:21.26,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...but for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.26,0:19:24.01,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...and for the rest of us, it will be a significant problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.47,0:19:26.94,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose that you can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.94,0:19:28.36,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...give me any more details, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.73,0:19:30.09,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.09,0:19:32.24,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, just think of it as a hint.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.69,0:19:34.43,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.99,0:19:37.31,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And that would be Snow White?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.72,0:19:38.39,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.15,0:19:40.44,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.67,0:19:50.26,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe I was able to wear this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.26,0:19:51.74,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't be able to do it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.19,0:19:55.12,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What other costumes did Haruhi make you wear?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.24,0:19:57.53,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.53,0:19:59.22,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.22,0:20:01.25,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, you'll find out soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.31,0:20:04.02,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll be going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.88,0:20:10.66,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,One last thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.20,0:20:13.98,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get too close to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.90,0:20:16.43,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell me one thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.03,0:20:19.31,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Asahina-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.80,0:20:21.40,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,How old are you right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.75,0:20:24.32,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Classified information.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.94,0:20:27.79,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Her smile was so brilliant that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.79,0:20:29.63,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...any person would fall in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.85,0:20:33.57,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's been so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.02,0:20:35.01,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So basically...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.01,0:20:37.43,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...the Asahina-san in high school right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.43,0:20:41.44,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...will return to her own time before long.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.44,0:20:45.58,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder how much time passed for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.58,0:20:47.61,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Based on her appearance, I'd say five years...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.61,0:20:48.95,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, three years?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.95,0:20:52.21,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Girls go through some dramatic changes once they're out of high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.65,0:20:53.77,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm pretty hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.77,0:20:55.14,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Guess I'll go back to the classroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.14,0:20:56.24,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.91,0:20:58.81,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.81,0:21:02.55,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see someone that looked a lot like Asahina-san on your way here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.89,0:21:05.39,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikuru Asahina's time-divergent variant.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.39,0:21:06.72,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I met her in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.72,0:21:07.68,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.68,0:21:09.87,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...you can also travel through time?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.87,0:21:11.82,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And that data whatever entity, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.82,0:21:13.43,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.43,0:21:16.61,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But time travel is not very difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.05,0:21:18.86,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you can tell me how it's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.32,0:21:21.90,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Words would be insufficient for conveying the concept...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.90,0:21:23.20,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...and you would not understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.20,0:21:24.46,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.46,0:21:25.34,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.34,0:21:27.41,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess that's settled.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.41,0:21:27.83,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Settled.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.93,0:21:30.05,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagato.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.05,0:21:31.21,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.59,0:21:33.00,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no need to thank me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.00,0:21:36.16,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryoko Asakura's abnormal behavior was my responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.16,0:21:36.67,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,My incompetence.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.19,0:21:40.17,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You really do look better without glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.18,0:21:47.51,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you go!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.51,0:21:50.27,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I waited to eat since I thought you'd be back soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.27,0:21:53.77,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you say that again, except like a childhood friend pretending to be angry to hide her embarrassment?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.77,0:21:55.24,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop sounding like an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.24,0:21:56.07,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.37,0:21:58.76,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked Okabe in the faculty office just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.76,0:22:02.36,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody knew about Asakura transferring until this morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.36,0:22:05.51,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,First thing this morning, a person claiming to be Asakura's father called...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.51,0:22:07.13,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...and said they had to move all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.13,0:22:08.45,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And guess where to?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.45,0:22:09.47,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Canada! Canada!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.47,0:22:10.23,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that even make sense?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.23,0:22:11.64,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds so made-up!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.64,0:22:12.12,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.43,0:22:15.67,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I asked for her contact information in Canada.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.67,0:22:16.90,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And guess what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.90,0:22:18.63,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They didn't even have that information!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.63,0:22:21.01,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You would normally leave your new contact information, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.01,0:22:23.05,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Something has to be up here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.05,0:22:23.89,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,How about no!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.89,0:22:26.98,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I was there I asked for Asakura's old address.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.98,0:22:29.06,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll go check it out after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.40,0:22:30.85,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We might learn something!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.67,0:22:35.32,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As always, she doesn't listen to anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.32,0:22:37.14,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, I'm not going to bother stopping her.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.14,0:22:39.83,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's the one wasting effort, not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.83,0:22:41.25,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You're coming with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.25,0:22:42.11,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why!?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.36,0:22:47.63,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And you call yourself a member of the SOS Brigade!?
